----------------------------------------------------

**Classes:**
- Wizard, 

**Spells:**
- Healing, Damage, Shield

Game Fundamentals:

- Each player is given 25 cards randomly (Spells and Unit Cards RNG)
- Play as many cards they want in a turn 
- Can activate up to three cards (defend and attack) 
- Mana system (should get full energy each turn) like elixir system card
